{"tid":926333,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"點解可以唔比工作影響情緒?","createTime":"2018-12-03T11:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T01:45:32.000Z","uid":95057,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0866912fed47edb2b0657d38b54517d768709cfe","tid":926333,"uid":95057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T11:12:09.000Z","msg":"返工好易比工作影響情緒<br />\n份工成日趕死線覺得好大壓力<br />\n比人話兩句又會放上心好耐<br />\n呢排好明顯影響到自己健康同身邊人嘅關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知喺香港返工邊度都係地獄<br />\n想問點樣可以令自己內心強大啲<br />\n點樣可以返工認真工作之餘 <br />\n唔會個人為工作嘅事擔心或緊張<br />\n(自己都覺好蠢但改唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n真心求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"878c45b3ff67e3044ba101e0e892672415e0fdcc","tid":926333,"uid":95057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T14:47:49.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95fcaf3de707e314a46524827e33220a60392a9","tid":926333,"uid":185734,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:01:44.000Z","msg":"轉下工，你就唔會咁念<br />\n每一個空間發生既事<br />\n只係短暫存在係個個空間<br />\n一但轉換，就不會再存在<br />\n無需事事放心中"},{"pid":"9aba5b01cee3e2f69e57d4d2efc13d7ec1b28928","tid":926333,"uid":138173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:10:09.000Z","msg":"點樣影響身邊人嘅關係？<br />\nbtw返返下就會習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02fa3944532311fe0365857bf3559ea138e87275","tid":926333,"uid":76404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f95fcaf3de707e314a46524827e33220a60392a9","tid":926333,"uid":185734,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:01:44.000Z","msg":"轉下工，你就唔會咁念<br />\n每一個空間發生既事<br />\n只係短暫存在係個個空間<br />\n一但轉換，就不會再存在<br />\n無需事事放心中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:14:06.000Z","msg":"師兄好似好多經歷"},{"pid":"23bfd8259ca930af6c6d92ea41e3e668ad85851f","tid":926333,"uid"