 />\n所以我努力令自己走去外國做"},{"pid":"2c2ebd84fe88d91eae44ba83a65844c6b41f4041","tid":926333,"uid":171594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:36:53.000Z","msg":"跟岩上司/老細都好重要<br />\n我上司岩岩做人老母<br />\n日日六點幾就閃人<br />\n<br />\n唔check email<br />\n冇wtsapp group<br />\n收工可以完全唔諗公司野"},{"pid":"d4972175e0f44b43566929a9d82d401a51c0913e","tid":926333,"uid":114866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66bd8ad99ccf52d24a6836675436b0235ed9cc07","tid":926333,"uid":95057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"23bfd8259ca930af6c6d92ea41e3e668ad85851f","tid":926333,"uid":114866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:19:12.000Z","msg":"我有同樣情況 而且只係啱啱返左2個月嘅fg<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:30:57.000Z","msg":"早你一兩年畢業<br />\n一開始我都是咁 <br />\n諗住做耐啲會習慣<br />\n<br />\n後來仲衰咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n社會新鮮人嘅毛病<br />\nWe are not alone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:42:55.000Z","msg":"我而家都係咁 諗住做多排睇下點<br />\n但同時有quit嘅念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b983660d4048e30bbd5d8573bb31b90a8c755a12","tid":926333,"uid":95057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"957fb19cb44afdd43982320f3de99f86902ef816","tid":926333,"uid":138173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66bd8ad99ccf52d24a6836675436b0235ed9cc07","tid":926333,"uid":95057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"23bfd8259ca930af6c6d92ea41e3e668ad85851f","tid":926333,"uid":114866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:19:12.000Z","msg":"我有同樣情況 而且只係啱啱返左2個月嘅fg<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:30:57.000Z","msg":"早你一兩年畢業<br />\n一開始我都是咁 <br />\n諗住做耐啲會習慣<br />\n<br />\n後來仲衰咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n社